WEBVTT

00:00:00.973 --> 00:00:04.107
2014 is a very special year for me:

00:00:04.107 --> 00:00:06.034
20 years as a consultant,

00:00:06.034 --> 00:00:07.706
20 years of marriage,

00:00:07.706 --> 00:00:10.887
and I'm turning 50 in one month.

00:00:10.887 --> 00:00:16.437
That means I was born in 1964
in a small town in Germany.

00:00:16.437 --> 00:00:18.155
It was a gray November day,

00:00:18.155 --> 00:00:20.035
and I was overdue.

00:00:20.035 --> 00:00:23.518
The hospital's maternity ward
was really stressed out

00:00:23.518 --> 00:00:28.023
because a lot of babies were born
on this gray November day.

